title: Scouts of the Air (1939 Adventure) Directed by Howard Bretherton

sources.title: Scouts of the Air (1939 Adventure) Directed by Howard Bretherton
sources.description:
Feel the exhilaration of watching one of Hollywood's first ever comic strip heroes onscreen. John Trent plays the legendary Tailspin Tommy in this classic thriller, where he tries helping out a juvenile delinquent. Trent as Tommy tries to help some juvenile delinquents by getting them interested in model airplane building. He encounters a special kid, Whitey, whom he takes under his wing.

Colorized version https://youtu.be/WXXJfHZImw4

Directors: Howard Bretherton
Starring: John Trent, Dennis Moore, Julius Tannen
Adventure • Romance • Drama
